                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9457" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2355</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">845 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">追“光”而行，驭“风”拓局：中际旭创的千亿市值飞跃之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Pursuing &quot;Light&quot;, Soaring High：The Growth Journey of Zhongji Innolight</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徐维东，王雯宇，范晓雨，包晗初</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中际旭创股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中际旭创；发展历程；跨界重组；协同效应；公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Zhongji Innolight; development history; cross-border reorganization;  synergy effect;  corporate governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">光模块作为光通信系统的核心部件，在实现数据高速传输方面扮演着至关重要的角色。受益于人工智能的爆发式成长，中际旭创作为全球光模块行业的佼佼者，总市值突破千亿元关口，成为业界瞩目的焦点。中际旭创的发展历程经历了多个重要节点：从乡镇电机厂起家，并成为国内外电机绕组装备制造业务领域首家上市公司；于传统业务衰败之际跨界光模块领域，通过深度整合协同构建完整产业链，厚筑技术护城河；以优异的公司治理，稳固核心技术人才，协调多方利益，打造“内外兼修”典范。中际旭创的成长史对我国高科技企业实现高质量发展具有重要借鉴意义。本案例旨在启发学生思考在快速变化的时代背景下，企业如何敏锐捕捉时代脉搏，精准把握战略机遇，通过产业布局和人员整合实现协同发展，同时也为其他企业战略转型提供指导和借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Optical modules are essential for high-speed data transmission. Zhongji Innolight has capitalized on the explosive growth of AI to consolidate its leadership in this field, achieving a market value surpassing 100 billion yuan. The company&#39;s development can be traced through several pivotal moments: starting as a township motor factory, it became the first listed company in its industry. Its transformation into the optical module sector was catalyzed by a successful acquisition. Zhongji Innolight further strengthened its core competencies through deep integration and synergy, and stabilized its talent pool through mature corporate governance. The company serves as an exemplary model for high-tech firms aiming for high-quality development, offering insights on seizing strategic opportunities and achieving coordinated growth in rapidly evolving environments. This case study aims to guide students in understanding these strategies and provide reference for other enterprises undergoing strategic transformations.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司战略管理》、《企业并购与重组》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生命周期理论；市场势力理论；并购整合理论；产业协同效应；委托代理理论；激励机制；并购风险理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
